### GET All Tasks
GET http://localhost:8081/api/tasks
Accept: application/json


### POST Create New Task
POST http://localhost:8081/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Setup Hono & TypeScript Backend",
    "description": "Initialize the project, install dependencies, and configure tsconfig.",
    "due_date": "2025-11-15"
}


### GET Task by ID (Replace {task_id} with an actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/tasks/{task_id}
Accept: application/json




### PUT Update Task - Move to In Progress (Replace {task_id} with an actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/tasks/{task_id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "stage": "in_progress"
}

### PUT Update Task - Update Title 
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Finished Backend Setup and Routing"
}



### DELETE Task by ID (Replace {task_id} with an actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/tasks/{task_id}